<view class="container">
  <view class="report-header">
    <text class="pet-name">{{report.petName}}的AI健康报告</text>
    <text class="risk-level {{report.riskLevel}}">风险等级：{{getRiskLevelText(report.riskLevel)}}</text>
  </view>
  <view class="section">
    <text class="section-title">可能存在的疾病</text>
    <view class="disease-list">
      <view wx:for="{{report.possibleDiseases}}" wx:key="*this" class="disease-item">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="section">
    <text class="section-title">健康提示</text>
    <view class="tip-list">
      <view wx:for="{{report.tips}}" wx:key="*this" class="tip-item">• {{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{report.recommendProducts.length > 0}}" class="section">
    <text class="section-title">推荐产品</text>
    <view class="product-list">
      <view wx:for="{{report.recommendProducts}}" wx:key="*this" class="product-item">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{report.recommendDoctors.length > 0}}" class="section">
    <text class="section-title">推荐医生</text>
    <view class="doctor-list">
      <view wx:for="{{report.recommendDoctors}}" wx:key="*this" class="doctor-item">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{report.recommendHospitals.length > 0}}" class="section">
    <text class="section-title">推荐医院</text>
    <view class="hospital-list">
      <view wx:for="{{report.recommendHospitals}}" wx:key="*this" class="hospital-item">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="disclaimer">
    <text>免责声明：以上分析和推荐仅供参考，不能替代专业医疗建议。具体情况请务必咨询专业兽医，在专业指导下进行护理或治疗。</text>
  </view>
</view>